Class DWGraph_DS.edges_direction

java.lang.Object
api.DWGraph_DS.edges_direction
Enclosing class:
DWGraph_DS
public static class DWGraph_DS.edges_direction
extends java.lang.Object
This private class represents all the edges getting out of a given node. uses a data structure from the type of HahMap.
